did.head: Overview
did.abstract: Harold Stein was an active member of the Filking community. He amassed a large collection of filk songs, zines, convention papers, and audio recordings.

physdesc.label: Extent
physdesc.extent: 34 boxes and an unknown number of terrabytes

note.p: The Harold Stein Filk Collection contains....
Most materials within the collection are within copyright. Permission to duplicate these materials is governed by United States copyright law.
The collection is open and available for research.
